🎯 CORE GOAL:

Build a production-grade mobile + backend system that acts as a daily AI business manager for small and medium businesses.

The system must answer daily:

👉 “What should I do TODAY to grow my business, why, and what result will I get?”

🏗️ SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE (MANDATORY)
Backend:
FastAPI (Python)
Async APIs
JWT Authentication
Database:
Urban Mode → PostgreSQL
Rural Mode → SQLite (fully isolated)
Cache:
Redis (for recommendations, sessions)
Background Jobs:
Celery (or FastAPI BackgroundTasks for MVP)
ML Layer:
Separate service/module:
Segmentation
Prediction
Recommendation Engine
Integrations:
SMS → Twilio / MSG91
WhatsApp → WhatsApp Business API
Notifications → Firebase Cloud Messaging
